    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0808a05"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>越州開元寺<persName key="A011561">丹甫</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0808a06"/><persName key="A011561">釋丹甫</persName>者，不知何許人也。性多警達，言必<lb
ed="T" n="0808a07"/>剛直，講授唯勤，執持雅正。<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>風土，律範淵<lb
ed="T" n="0808a08"/>府也。<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>之唱導，從之者若玄金之就礠石<lb
ed="T" n="0808a09"/>焉。本習業於<persName key="A011564">亘文律師</persName>法集，<persName key="A011564">文</persName>即<persName key="A011073">省躬</persName>之游<lb
ed="T" n="0808a10"/>夏也，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>即<persName key="A011073">躬</persName>之嗣孫。順正命章，斡通祕賾<ptr target="#n331"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0808a11"/>越自<persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>、<persName key="A010815">玄儼</persName>之後，罕能追躡，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>之聲塵<lb
ed="T" n="0808a12"/>邁于前烈。然爾時<persName key="A011632">允文</persName>匠手，<ref type="person" target="#A000747">相部</ref>風行，<persName key="A011561">甫</persName>介<lb
ed="T" n="0808a13"/>于大律之間，行事之時，草從風偃焉。<date from-iso="0870" key="j20389922040147" to-iso="0873">咸通末</date><lb
ed="T" n="0808a14"/>出門生<persName key="A011562">智章</persName>等傳講，今亦法嗣存焉。或聞<lb
ed="T" n="0808a15"/>著《手記》，尋且未獲，吁，惜哉！</p>
